xdi2.core.impl.keyvalue

Interface KeyValueStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractKeyValueStore, BDBKeyValueStore, MapKeyValueStore, PropertiesKeyValueStore

    public interface KeyValueStore
    The key/value based graph storage implementations needs a KeyValueStore to function. This defines basic operations on a key/value pair based datastore.
